{"tid":1012774,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣] 華航機師今晨6時啟動罷工","createTime":"2019-02-07T23:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T15:11:45.000Z","uid":65346,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"baf79577c52d69bfd2c679822102b7b60fccee47","tid":1012774,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T23:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190208/20608688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190208%2F20608688&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcqDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=933b30d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190208%2F20608688&h=4453f019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190208/20608688</a><br />\n【本報訊】華航勞資談判破裂。機師工會華航分會宣佈，今日清晨6時開始罷工，預計有700名機師配合，目前正值春節高峯期，機師工會發動罷工，預計會造成旅客嚴重延誤。<br />\n華航發聲明稱無意讓步<br />\n桃園、松山及高雄機場升降的航班將受今次工業行動影響，今天香港來往桃園及高雄機場的航班分別有18班及8班。機師工會理事陳蓓蓓表示，目前已經發出罷工簡訊，並將會持續回收會員的證件，預計至少有700名華航機師配合工會罷工行動。<br />\n<br />\n華航發言人劉朝洋表示，稍後將召開內部會議，討論應對方式；至於會影響多少航班，劉朝洋並無說明，僅表示要看調度後才能估計，預計明早會發對外新聞稿。據了解，華航在春節期間除原定正班機再加上加班機，每日約有近200班航班。<br />\n<br />\n交通部昨晚也發聲明指，部長林佳龍已指示成立緊急應變中心，將持續努力盼促成勞資雙方對話溝通，不放棄任何機會。<br />\n<br />\n機師工會昨天中午發佈新聞稿表示，雖然交通部出面協調，但華航仍然拒絕接受改善疲勞航班等訴求，機師工會迫於無奈，隨時準備發動罷工。華航昨晚發聲明，稱對於機師工會訴求仍毫不讓步，並以財務精算、法定勞務派遣方式一一反駁。"},{"pid":"422a4b71567b789e03b27f4fa74ddcaa96b09322","tid":1012774,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":36,"score":-35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T23:47:31.000Z","msg":"我有懷疑空姐幫肥人抹屎單野<br />\n係空姐刻意安排搏同情...<br />\n台灣人就係 like R 著數"},{"pid":"dd346aabcead1e8e6209836b6e37f7f84f363e14","tid":1012774,"uid":45332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"422a4b71567b789e03b27f4fa74ddcaa96b09322","tid":1012774,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":36,"score":-35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T23:47:31.000Z","msg":"我有懷疑空姐幫肥人抹屎單野<br />\n係空姐刻意安排搏同情...<br />\n台灣人就係 like R 著數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:12:42.000Z","msg":"果單唔係長榮咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e647b3c7316b82b0b3ea768d7d1134b47044433","tid":1012774,"uid":20658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"422a4b71567b789e03b27f4fa74ddcaa96b09322","tid":1012774,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":36,"score":-35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T23:47:31.000Z","msg":"我有懷疑空姐幫肥人抹屎單野<br />\n係空姐刻意安排搏同情...<br />\n台灣人就係 like R 著數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:18:18.000Z","msg":"二間公司黎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792daa9b6da204f311eec96efd878e71fe032e1c","tid":1012774,"uid":165598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:21:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"950445343ce2a87db5725f546987153d08874e63","tid":1012774,"uid":192528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"422a4b71567b789e03b27f4fa74ddcaa96b09322","tid":1012774,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":36,"score":-35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T23:47:31.000Z","msg":"我有懷疑空姐幫肥人抹屎單野<br />\n係空姐刻意安排搏同情...<br />\n台灣人就係 like R 著數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:32:03.000Z","msg":"新年流流衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc4aad1a13fbacae56adc2278656f9f9cec3f95","tid":1012774,"uid":159308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:35:29.000Z","msg":"我中Ｌ左，而家搭CX<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V2auvUL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2auvUL.png&h=11ed9c1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"616b8f172ca40904e528ac75ca5123bc85dbd533","tid":1012774,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dc4aad1a13fbacae56